caption.title: Effect of the anti-DENV scFv on DENV-2 GE in three independent mosquito lines.
caption.p: DENV-2 GE are shown below for WT, TADV-A, TADV-B, and TADV-C mosquito lines following a blood meal infected with the DENV-2 ET300 strain. Midgut samples were collected 4 dpi, and GE were determined using real-time RT-qPCR and calculated using previously published methods.
